title: Smell What the Rock is Cookin'
itunes:title: Smell What the Rock is Cookin'
description:
The Rock called Anthony's latest special "brilliant" and Gregg pushes for more love and positivity on the show. Anthony, Gregg and Erica find out what "type of bitch" they are according to Cosmo and Anthony wonders how many people you'd have to murder to make people forget about OJ Simpson.
